DOCS:
Reference documentation: http://plplot.sourceforge.net/docbook-manual/plplot-html-5.9.0/
Plplot homepage: http://plplot.sourceforge.net
Plplot wiki: http://www.miscdebris.net/plplot_wiki/index.php?title=Main_Page
Exampels are placed in: /h/masar/plplot-5.9.0/examples/c

Suggestions:
- Plot days instead of timesteps
- "Legends?" for the lables?

COMPILATION: 

Depends on:
- plplot (-lplplotd)
- libutil
- libhash
- libecl
- zlib

For debugging, run for example 
csh% ./plot.x -debug


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Rememer to set:
csh% setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH /h/masar/plplot-5.9.0/Compilation/lib
or
bash% export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/h/masar/plplot-5.9.0/Compilation/lib"


Some notes on TrueType fonts:

The way to change the symbol (for example when plotting points) font is:

setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_FONT_DIR /h/masar/sfd/
setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_SYMBOL_BOLD_FONT FreeSerifBold.ttf
setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_SYMBOL_BOLD_ITALIC_FONT FreeSerifBoldItalic.ttf
setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_SYMBOL_BOLD_OBLIQUE_FONT FreeSerifBoldItalic.ttf
setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_SYMBOL_FONT FreeSerif.ttf
setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_SYMBOL_ITALIC_FONT FreeSerifItalic.ttf
setenv PLPLOT_FREETYPE_SYMBOL_OBLIQUE_FONT FreeSerifItalic.ttf

For more in depth work with the fonts in the plot, one can look at:
http://plplot.sourceforge.net/docbook-manual/plplot-html-5.9.0/characters.html#fci

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMPILE INSTRUCTIONS FOR PLPLOT ITSELF:

First you need to have cmake installed.
It has been compiled already and you can find it in /h/masar/cmake/bin.

Basic instructions: http://www.miscdebris.net/plplot_wiki/index.php?title=Linux
Modifications: 

Use the curses Interface for CMake:
csh% ccmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/h/masar/plplot-5.9.0/Compilation/ -DCMAKE_VERBOSE_MAKEFILE=ON -DHAVE_FREETYPE=ON ..

Now there is a few variables that has to be changed:
ENABLE_f77=OFF
ENABLE_f95=OFF
FREETYPE_INCLUDE_DIR=/usr/include/freetype2
WITH_FREETYPE=ON
PL_FREETYPE_FONT_PATH=/h/masar/sfd/

csh% make && make install

